29:11.626 --> 29:14.129
<i>He's all over
the plate right now.</i>

29:19.676 --> 29:21.511
Now you got the idea.

29:27.308 --> 29:29.060
<i>Down goes Tuttle.</i>

29:29.144 --> 29:30.228
<i>What a knockdown pitch
that was.</i>

29:30.311 --> 29:32.313
<i>There's a message
being delivered.</i>

29:32.397 --> 29:34.732
<i>Yankee Stadium is
like a schoolyard</i>

29:34.816 --> 29:38.027
<i>and Bill Murdie looks like
a teacher who sees trouble.</i>

29:39.028 --> 29:42.031
<i>They say in every great
athlete there's a mean streak</i>

29:42.115 --> 29:44.284
<i>and Billy Chapel's
